room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: This activity was very interesting. I enjoyed the detail used and working as a group. This is a great team building exercise with plenty of surprises throughout the event. Two thumbs up.

room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: Went with some friends and had a blast at entrap games! You should check it out I recommended it.

room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: We got out of Off Limits on sisters night out! Lots of fun! Sadie was the best!

room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: Had a great time! The room was a challenge which we all wanted, but when needed the clues were enough to keep us moving. Highly recommend for team building, date night, family outing (teenagers+). We would love to go back!

room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: There's no better way to celebrate an anniversary than getting locked in a room with four complete strangers. We had a blast doing "Off Limits" and will definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: We had a great time and the staff was SO friendly and helpful. We are planning our next escape already!!

room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
review: I have done escape room with several different companies and this one is by far the best! Rooms have enough puzzles to solve that it is challenging but they are much more logical and well executed. Sadie was freat, would definitely return!
